## Harness

This project uses [Claude Code Harness](https://github.com/OWNER/claude-code-harness) v{{HARNESS_VERSION}}.
For guardrail rules, agents, and commands, see the bundled `@CLAUDE-HARNESS.md`
inside the plugin, or run `/harness-setup` inside a Claude Code session.

Configuration lives in `./harness.config.json` at the project root.
Edit it to tune `protectedDirectories`, `protectedEnvVarNames`, etc.

## Task management

`Plans.md` is the single source of truth for outstanding work.
Use labels: `[feature]`, `[fix]`, `[improve]`, `[test]`, `[docs]`, `[refactor]`, `[security]`.

## Development workflow

| Step | Skill |
|------|-------|
| Plan | `/harness-plan` |
| Implement | `/harness-work` |
| Review | `/harness-review` |
| Release | `/harness-release` |
| Configure | `/harness-setup` |
